 consider if anything else could be going on here.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.10799,0.086765,0.081576,0.074339,0.076141,0.079306,0.082821,0.092244,0.083487,0.057617,0.060532,0.11718],"unified_progress":[0.19923,0.075674,0.063554,0.064168,0.073596,0.073621,0.10458,0.08339,0.080753,0.0646,0.05999,0.056838]},{"section":11,"text":"They said there's no spasticity or other abnormalities in the neurological exam.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.071806,0.079561,0.086485,0.09473,0.097846,0.096497,0.094057,0.088717,0.084821,0.084795,0.072979,0.047704],"unified_progress":[0.067581,0.097019,0.069481,0.093751,0.098284,0.098255,0.094012,0.091528,0.085456,0.080041,0.070575,0.054016]},{"section":12,"text":"So, it doesn't seem like there's a general motor issue affecting the whole body.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034956,0.056153,0.076504,0.091849,0.098771,0.10343,0.1048,0.10305,0.099572,0.096549,0.0818,0.052573],"unified_progress":[0.041762,0.066775,0.081665,0.092724,0.096254,0.095327,0.098668,0.097586,0.095199,0.091769,0.079713,0.06256]},{"section":13,"text":"And their vision seems fine too, as visual acuity and ophthalmoscopy are normal.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031851,0.057136,0.082089,0.10561,0.11636,0.1167,0.10991,0.097523,0.086996,0.081105,0.068249,0.046469],"unified_progress":[0.040409,0.067871,0.084443,0.094827,0.10181,0.10004,0.098078,0.095394,0.096434,0.083841,0.073978,0.062866]},{"section":14,"text":"This makes me even more confident that we're dealing with something specific to the eyes rather than a broader neurological problem.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027207,0.050734,0.070631,0.086548,0.094325,0.099909,0.10083,0.097375,0.093552,0.093587,0.096912,0.088386],"unified_progress":[0.032842,0.056506,0.072081,0.083289,0.088185,0.089776,0.096116,0.097048,0.097125,0.096829,0.096561